title: Placido Domingo - The Latin Album Collection (musicfromrizzo)
description:
Here is perhaps one of the truly greatest singers anywhere in the world with some great music for the soul. 100 songs

My favourites in this Latin collection we bring you here include: Siboney, Solamente una vez Perfidia, Siempre en mi corazon, Adoro, Caballo viejo (included in a medley here), Aquellos ojos verdes, Manhã de carnaval and Quiéreme mucho

Enjoy and please seed for the family at large
with thanks - gracias indeed

Michael Rizzo Chessman
(musicfromrizzo)
